  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00432', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-099-9cd45b90', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-06', NULL, 'essay', '甲、乙、丙三人共有土地一筆，甲將其應有部分 1/3 設定抵押於 A 銀行。嗣甲、乙、
